## 📱 Responsive Rules
1. Default (Desktop):
   ```css
   .app-container {
       width: 100%;
       max-width: var(--embed-width);
   }
   .left-nav { width: var(--nav-width); }
   .content-area { width: var(--content-width); }
   ```

2. Embedded Mode:
   ```css
   .embedded .app-header,
   .embedded .top-banner {
       display: none !important;
   }
   .embedded .app-container {
       height: 100vh;
       margin: 0;
   }
   ```

3. Live Mode:
   ```css
   /* Collapsed navigation */
   .live .left-nav {
       width: 60px;
   }
   .live .content-area {
       width: calc(100% - 60px);
   }
   ```

